'''FreeAdvice'''是总部位于[[美国|美国]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[索萨利托_(加利福尼亚州)|索萨利托]]的[[免费|免费]][[法律|法律]][[信息|信息]]网站<ref name="Singh2005">{{cite book|author=Douglas A. Singh|title=Effective Management of Long-term Care Facilities|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=j1JxSKao-awC&pg=PA114|year=2005|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|isbn=978-0-7637-4801-2|pages=114–|access-date=2020-07-14|archive-date=2020-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714065603/https://books.google.com/books?id=j1JxSKao-awC&pg=PA114|dead-url=no}}</ref>，隶属于[[Advice公司|Advice公司]]（Advice Company）<ref name="LemingDickinson2015">{{cite book|author1=Michael R. Leming|author2=George E. Dickinson|title=Understanding Dying, Death, and Bereavement|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=gKCaBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA596|date=1 January 2015|publisher=Cengage Learning|isbn=978-1-305-53761-3|pages=596–|access-date=2020-07-14|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722110741/https://books.google.com/books?id=gKCaBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA596|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由[[格里·戈德斯霍勒|格里·戈德斯霍勒]]（Gerry Goldsholle）[[律师|律师]]于1997年创立<ref>{{cite book|title=California Law Business|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FX05AQAAIAAJ|year=2000|publisher=Daily Journal Corporation|pages=17-|access-date=2020-07-14|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722110605/https://books.google.com/books?id=FX05AQAAIAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该网站[[域名|域名]]FreeAdvice.com注册于1996年3月26日<ref>{{cite web| url=https://whois.domaintools.com/freeadvice.com| title=Whois Record for FreeAdvice.com| work=[[WHOIS|WHOIS]]| accessdate=2020-07-14| archive-date=2020-07-15| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715043347/https://whois.domaintools.com/freeadvice.com| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

FreeAdvice.com获得过诸多奖项奖项，包括2000年被《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》评选为“最佳网络”<ref>{{cite web|last1=Newcomb|first1=Kelly|title=Legal Advice|url=https://www.forbes.com/forbes/2000/0522/6512128a.html|website=Forbes.com|publisher=|date=May 21, 2000|accessdate=2020-07-14|archive-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716113552/https://www.forbes.com/forbes/2000/0522/6512128a.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2004年被《[[个人电脑杂志|个人电脑杂志]]》（ PC Magazine）评为“50个最佳网站之一”<ref>{{cite web|author=Don Willmott|title=50 from the Best of the Internet:FreeAdvice|url=https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,1516962,00.asp|access-date=2020-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050408020608/http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,1759,1516962,00.asp|archive-date=2005-04-08|url-status=|df=|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及“1000个最佳网站中的100个特色网站之一”<ref>{{cite web|author=Don Willmott|title=50 from the Best of the Internet|url=https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,1516962,00.asp|access-date=2020-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050316020258/http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,4149,1522131,00.asp|archive-date=2005-03-16|url-status=|df=|dead-url=no}}</ref>，被《[[埃克森斯杂志|埃克森斯杂志]]》（Access Magazine）评为2009年度法律网站<ref>{{cite web|title=FreeAdvice|url=http://familyfirst.com/freeadvice.html|website=Family First|publisher=Socrates Digital, LLC|accessdate=29 August 2016|archive-date=2017-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170207064423/http://familyfirst.com/freeadvice.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2001年被《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》<ref>{{cite web|last1=Lee|first1=Jennifer|title=Legal Aid Online; Web's Law Library: A Partial Catalog|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2001/02/22/technology/legal-aid-online-web-s-law-library-a-partial-catalog.html|website=The New York Times|publisher=The New York Times Company|accessdate=29 August 2016|archive-date=2020-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714073325/https://www.nytimes.com/2001/02/22/technology/legal-aid-online-web-s-law-library-a-partial-catalog.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、1999年被《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》<ref>{{cite web|last1=Schmittq|first1=Richard|title=A Growing Number of Sites Dispense Legal Advice Online|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB933556084181501147|website=Wall Street Journal|publisher=Dow Jones & Company|accessdate=29 August 2016|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715165338/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB933556084181501147|dead-url=no}}</ref>、1998年被《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》的法律网站评论所认可<ref>{{cite web|last1=Meng|first1=Nancie|title=Tax Time Links|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/business/longterm/tax/links.htm|website=Washington Post|publisher=The Washington Post Company|accessdate=29 August 2016|archive-date=2017-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170207041605/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/business/longterm/tax/links.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

